name: Vampirella
description: This is a model that's based on the character Vampirella from the comic books with the same name. Tends to work best at 0.6. This model was trained on NAI anime-full-pruned and generated in Anything5. Made with the Kohya tool for AI Training through google colab. Any suggestions to improve or recommended things for the data set would be appreciated.
